title: Zumiez Store Locations, US 12.12.2007
name: Zumiez Store Locations, US 12.12.2007
description: This datset displays the locations for over 270 Zumiez retail stores throughout the United States. Zumiez is a retail store that specializes in clothing, gear, and accessories associated with the action sports industry. This includes skateboarding, Snowboarding, and surfing. This data was collected from the Zumiez Webpage at: www.zumiez.com and using the data collected from the store locater, the data was geocoded according to the address in order to find the latitude and longitude coordinates. This data was accessed on December 12, 2007.
